(4, 42, 'Byron Banks', 'c226432@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 07:57:51', '2017-06-14 07:57:51', 'I loved this place - very quiet in comparison to other places in Campania! Will come here during my next vacation.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(5, 42, 'Misty Mason', 'c229880@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 07:59:02', '2017-06-14 07:59:02', 'I agree, a wonderful place to enjoy the nature and away from noisy cities.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 4, 0),
(6, 42, 'Nathan Reynolds', 'c225547@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:00:34', '2017-06-14 08:00:34', 'This is the best place in Campania! Wonderful service,  always clean pool and lots of green places around it! A good combination of water and green lives.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(7, 40, 'Stacy Palmer', 'c225985@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:01:55', '2017-06-14 08:01:55', 'I spend here an unforgettable summer vocation with my family. I''d recommend it to big groups and for a long term.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(8, 38, 'Byron Banks', 'c226432@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:03:36', '2017-06-14 08:03:36', 'I''ve never been to Liguria before, but this villa made me love it even more.  Cool nature and cool house - all you need for comfort and luxury living.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(9, 38, 'Misty', 'c229880@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:04:55', '2017-06-14 08:04:55', 'Definitely - this villa bring so many harmony, it''s eco-friendly and offers so many modern things, I enjoyed staying here with friends for weekends.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 8, 0),
(10, 38, 'Nathan Reynolds', 'c225547@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:06:01', '2017-06-14 08:06:01', 'Misty, is it suitable for weekends as well? I thought it''s for a long term stay only. did not you have any problems?', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 9, 0),
(11, 36, 'Misty Mason', 'c229880@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:07:56', '2017-06-14 08:07:56', 'So special place - for lovers of ancient villas! You''ll definitely spend your warmest winter here.  thanks for such an awesome offer.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(12, 36, 'Nathan Reynolds', 'c225547@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:08:46', '2017-06-14 08:08:46', 'Beautiful cottage, thanks for the service and help in transfer!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(13, 34, 'Byron Banks', 'c226432@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:09:53', '2017-06-14 08:09:53', 'A nice place to spend the summer - I recommend to all beachfront lovers!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(14, 114, 'Byron Banks', 'c226432@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:12:19', '2017-06-14 08:12:19', 'I did not expect visiting gardens, but wanted to so something unusual - Vignanello garden is just for it! Great tour, thanks for discounts!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
(15, 110, 'Misty Mason', 'c229880@trbvn.com', '', '69.39.234.2', '2017-06-14 08:14:12', '2017-06-14 08:14:12', 'I always dreamed of visiting Italian castles and with a help of this discount my dream came true! Thanks, villa owners!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
