(36, 1, '2017-06-09 14:05:52', '2017-06-09 14:05:52', 'Cottage Monte Bianco in Aosta Valley is a well-decorated, warm and fully functional country cottage perfect for your winter vacation.\r\n\r\nThis mountain cottage is made up of stone and timber built on two storeys, with a large living room, glass window, a couch for two people and a bathroom with sauna.\r\n\r\nThe second storeys features a double bedroom. There is also a queen bed. There is a large garden with mountain view outdoors. You may also use a porch equipped with BBQ and a wooden table.\r\n\r\nThe site is located on the pleasant hills between Aosta Valley mountains. We have currently added two beds, set up in a wonderful Indian teepe available for two extra guests in addition to the four ones. Four beds for children are still the same.', 'Alps Mountains Winter Cottage Monte Bianco in Aosta Valley', 'Cottage Monte Bianco in Aosta Valley is well-decorated, warm and fully functional country cottage perfect for your winter vacation. ', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'deluxe-ski-in-ski-out-aspen-townhouse', '', '', '2017-06-14 09:00:56', '2017-06-14 09:00:56', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/?post_type=mphb_room_type&#038;p=36', 0, 'mphb_room_type', '', 2),
